repos.name: CarCare-Reminder
repos.description: CarCare Reminder is a modern, elegant, and user-friendly mobile app designed to help car owners effortlessly manage their vehicle maintenance. The app provides automated reminders for essential services like oil changes, brake checks, battery replacements, tire rotations, and other consumables, based on time or mileage.

repos.name: Weather-Pulse
repos.description: WeatherPulse is a modern, clean, and visually stunning mobile weather app that delivers real-time weather information with beautiful, dynamic animated backgrounds. The app automatically detects your location and provides accurate weather data, while also allowing you to search for any location worldwide with autocomplete suggestions.

repos.name: OptiTravel
repos.description: The app calculates the most efficient route between attractions using the Travelling Salesman Problem (TSP) based on the user's hotel location, implementing nearest-neighbor first and then 2-opt refinement. It should provide multiple itinerary suggestions based on the places the user selects.

repos.name: MYHealth-Risk
repos.description: Malaysia-based Health Risk Calculator that follows MOH guidelines, includes Malaysian Framingham Risk Score interpretation, local BMI categories, blood pressure classification, diabetes risk assessment, and lifestyle recommendation

repos.name: LeaveSync
repos.description: Monitor staff leave, public holidays, and connected leave in one shared calendar. Stay informed, plan better, and avoid overlapping leave
